data.title: Super Star Krishna Movies List
data.meta_description: Super Star Krishna Movies List - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document appears to be a list of Telugu films from 1965 to 1973 featuring various female actors. It includes information on 94 films, listing the movie name, lead heroine, director, and date of release. The films starred popular actresses of the time like Vijaya Nirmala, Vanisri, Jamuna, and Kanchana. The directors included many prominent names in the Telugu film industry like Adurthi Subba Rao, K. Viswanath, and V. Ramachandra Rao.
